  • Field Details

    • type

      String type

    • id

      String id

    • version

      String version
      LDR version specification version, in the format: <Major>.<minor>.

      When there are changes that do not break backward compatibility, the minor version will be increased, otherwise, the Major version will be increased.

    • activityId

      String activityId
      Activity identifier, generally.
      • In session scenarios, it is the session identifier.
      • In single event scenarios, where there is no session (e.g., provisioning, top-ups), it is the event identifier.
      This field is used to associate segments of the same activity.

    • activityType

      String activityType
      Activity type (e.g. PRV, policy N7, authorization N5, N28).

    • activitySubType

      String activitySubType
      Activity subtype (e.g. for PRV: CREATE_ACCCOUNT, CREATE_PRODUCT, UPDATE_ACCOUNT, UPDATE_PRODUCT)
